page_title: How to migrate to OpenAI Python v1.x
page_description: Learn about migrating to the latest release of the OpenAI Python library with Azure OpenAI.
chunk_content: Known issues- `DALL-E3` is fully supported with the latest 1.x release. `DALL-E2` can be used with 1.x by making the following modifications to your code.- `embeddings_utils.py` which was used to provide functionality like cosine similarity for semantic text search is no longer part of the OpenAI Python API library.- You should also check the active GitHub Issues for the OpenAI Python library.
